data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the desirable RiverPark Dunes area, where spacious living meets convenience! This 2002 sq. ft. home offers an ideal combination of comfort and style, featuring:  Open and bright great room with laminate flooring, New carpet in bedrooms for a cozy feel, Fresh interior paint throughout (except for 2 bedrooms), Well-appointed kitchen with granite countertops and a large center island, Tons of storage space for all your culinary needs.  Primary bedroom w/ a spacious layout, 2 sinks gorgeous tile shower + a large walk-in closet. The 3 additional bedrooms are on the opposite wing  w/a spacious bath featuring a tiled shower/tub and a separate laundry room with cabinets. Garage Perks: Extra-large three-car garage for ample parking and storage Premium Features: Top-of-the-line Kinetico potassium-based osmotic system Outside spigots for car washing without water spots Vivant Security System Outdoor Oasis:  Covered pavilion + separate uncovered patio for entertaining. Sprinklers in the front and back yards for easy lawn maintenance Raised garden beds with a drip system for your green thumb Nestled in the RiverPark Dunes area, across from the park No association fees - no dues! Call Today to Make This Dream Home Yours!
